{"tid":1102452,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"EPIC 出爾反爾？玩家不滿《ANNO 1800》臨時改 EPIC 獨佔","createTime":"2019-04-11T16:43:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-22T06:59:06.000Z","uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"718acdd7bccf49a60b9c1a76601466f6adbbffd0","tid":1102452,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T16:43:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.esports.yahoo.com/出爾反爾？epic-執行長將繼續簽屬獨佔遊戲，不管是-090025254.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.esports.yahoo.com%2F%E5%87%BA%E7%88%BE%E5%8F%8D%E7%88%BE%EF%BC%9Fepic-%E5%9F%B7%E8%A1%8C%E9%95%B7%E5%B0%87%E7%B9%BC%E7%BA%8C%E7%B0%BD%E5%B1%AC%E7%8D%A8%E4%BD%94%E9%81%8A%E6%88%B2%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8D%E7%AE%A1%E6%98%AF-090025254.html&d=Cuyai%2BbkQ%2BZKjwazMoctzkcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=66544700\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.esports.yahoo.com/出爾反爾？epic-執行長將繼續簽屬獨佔遊戲，不管是-090025254.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/TimSweeneyEpic/status/1112814353496117248\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTimSweeneyEpic%2Fstatus%2F1112814353496117248&d=Cuyai%2BbkQ%2BZKjwazMoctzkcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=6b66ae17\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTimSweeneyEpic%2Fstatus%2F1112814353496117248&h=f25e624f\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/TimSweeneyEpic/status/1112814353496117248</a><br />\n<br />\nEpic Games 在上個月中的 GDC 2019 上才剛表示不會再重複《Metro Exodus》的錯誤，搶在其他平台上市之前與廠商簽下獨佔協議。然而在 4 月 16 日即將上市的《ANNO 1800》卻又在發售前改成 Epic Games 平台獨佔，對此行為 Epic 執行長則改口說：「一切由發行商自己決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」。<br />\n<br />\n玩家對於 Epic Games 出爾反爾的行為當然非常不滿，直接跑去 Epic 執行長 Tim Sweeney 的推特上質問，並貼出當時 GDC 上的訪談文章，大罵 Tim Sweeney 說謊。而 Tim Sweeney 則回應：「從 GDC 結束以來，我們對此進行了大量的討論。無論遊戲是否已經或計畫在 Steam 上推出，Epic 都願意接受任何開發者與發行商簽署獨佔協議。」<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/lo/api/res/1.2/iLEEI.0fCiKZvQUz9LmsbQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9ZXNwb3J0O3NtPTE7dz04ODA-/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/a1581c32f72fdd09609dfe5d35bf2fac\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Flo%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FiLEEI.0fCiKZvQUz9LmsbQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9ZXNwb3J0O3NtPTE7dz04ODA-%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2Fa1581c32f72fdd09609dfe5d35bf2fac&h=c1f2b564&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n當然 Tim Sweeney 這樣的說法並不被接受，因為有網友發文表示：「《ANNO 1800》的發行商 Ubisoft，他們有自己專屬的平台 Uplay，不需要 12% 手續費，甚至比在 Epic Games 上購買更便宜，若不是因為騰訊（指 Epic Games）花大錢購買的話，那他們為何要選擇上  Epic Games 的平台呢？」"},{"pid":"3e13128af51619aa696ea1408e791708b1d23972","tid":1102452,"uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T16:45:21.000Z","msg":"而或許是為了平息玩家的憤怒，Ubisoft 宣佈直到 4 月 16 日發售之前玩家都可以在 Steam 上購買，並支援購買者後續的全部更新，但正式發售後只有 Uplay 與 Epic Games 平台上可以直接買到數位版本。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sspPJpH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsspPJpH.png&h=66a4eb26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://store.steampowered.com/app/916440/Anno_1800/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F916440%2FAnno_1800%2F&d=Cuyai%2BbkQ%2BZKjwazMoctzkcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=58416df0\" target=\"_blank\">https://store.steampowered.com/app/916440/Anno_1800/</a>"},{"pid":"be7128c607d9093566b644b4d18ec9aae4f853ef","tid":1102452,"uid":210693,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T18:35:09.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母啲中資成撚日都想做爛個市"},{"pid":"dffe8446abc7b43734da1356f5f81ce10d031b7e","tid":1102452,"uid":75193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T18:45:23.000Z","msg":"屌 anno都係咁 唔撚玩住"},{"pid":"bc06bbb96deb77a95e3096d78776c4b3892d508a","tid":1102452,"uid":116289,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T18:49:40.000Z","msg":"垃撚圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8d39a7df634df1